'''''Kuva Kuva Vaathugal''''' ({{lang-en|The Ducks}}) is a [[1984 in film|1984]] [[Tamil language|Tamil]]  [[Cinema of India|Indian]] [[feature film]] [[Film director|directed]] by [[Manivannan]] for [[Panchu Arunachalam]]' s Panchu Movies. The film stars [[Sivakumar]], [[Sulakshana (actress)|Sulakshana]], [[Pandiyan (actor)|Pandiyan]] and [[Ilavarasi]] in the lead roles.<ref>{{cite web|title=Kuva Kuva Vaathugal LP Vinyl Records|url=http://musicalaya.net/imgviewer.php?mod=lpcovers/495/3/1/1|publisher=musicalaya|accessdate=2014-05-01|}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=Kuva Kuva Vaathugal full movie|url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=4WncPWebFxE|publisher=youtube|accessdate=2015-08-26|}}</ref>

