==Soundtrack==
Soundtrack was composed by Ilaiyaraja and lyrics were written by Panchu Arunachalam.<ref>http://play.raaga.com/tamil/album/Kuva-Kuva-Vathukkal-songs-t0002776</ref>
*"Nenachen Nenachen" - [[Vani Jayaram]]
*"Paayum Puli" - [[S. Janaki]]
*"Pollatha Aasai" - [[S. P. Balasubrahmanyam|SPB]], Vani Jayaram
*"Thenil" - Krishnachandran, S. Janaki

